          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-8 col-centered">
              <p class="subhead">
                The Fellowship begins with an in-person convening at GLG’s headquarters in New York City, where Fellows join our learning community and learn how to use the GLG platform. During the convening, Fellows work with GLG to identify the top challenges facing their organizations and set learning objectives to meet those challenges.
              </p>
              <br>
              <br>
            </div>
