              <br>
              <p class="highlight">
                <strong>Learning</strong><br>
                Tailored learning opportunities include phone consultations with subject matter experts, in-person meetings, roundtable discussions, teleconferences, and workshops.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
              <img src="/img/impact-learning.jpg" class="img-responsive">
              <br>
              <p class="highlight">
                <strong>Strategic Support</strong><br>
                Dedicated GLG Research Managers serve as thought partners for Fellows and their management teams. Research Managers design engagements that provide insight to inform strategy, address challenges, and help Fellows’ organizations continue to grow.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
              <img src="/img/impact-events.jpg" class="img-responsive">
              <br>
              <p class="highlight">
                <strong>Events</strong><br>
                Fellows and their teams have access to GLG’s rich ongoing events offering throughout the year, in addition to custom learning engagements.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
